OL,3,CHeatwave and World Cup shape spending
OL,4,Cfigures for June
OL,6,FOnline sales soared in June as
OL,7,Fconsumers shopped from home to beat
OL,8,Fthe heat, with electric fans and
OL,9,Fpaddling pools proving best sellers.
OL,11,FTotal retail sales across the UK were
OL,12,Fup 1.9% year on year in June, boosted
OL,13,Fsignificantly by a 5.1% increase in
OL,14,Fonline sales of products other than
OL,15,Ffood, according to the British Retail
OL,16,FConsortium (BRC)-KPMG data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
