OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784002678
OL,3,CHeatwave and World Cup shape spending
OL,4,Cfigures for June
OL,6,F"Looking ahead to the second half of
OL,7,F2026, we expect growth to pick up
OL,8,Fmodestly, as improving consumer
OL,9,Fsentiment and reduced uncertainty are
OL,10,Fpartially offset by the temporary
OL,11,Finflation bump."
